{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act27side", "eventName": "火山旅夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SL-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "雨啊，雨啊，快離開", "storyInfo": "在一場午夜幻夢中，艾雅法拉與兩隻非常像自己父母的小黑羊度過了夢幻的一晚。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g9_purewhitevolcano_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dream", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$bar_intro", "key": "$bar_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕陽似乎是這家小店的最後一個客人，但站在櫃檯後的不再是熟悉的老人，而是一隻咖啡色的生物。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它旋轉著研磨機的手把，咖啡的香氣和細碎的豆末飛進空氣中。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唱片慢慢地轉著，擴音器悠悠地唱。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，歡迎光臨。", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前好像從來沒有見過您，您是剛到這裡的嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是的，因為我沒有昨天的記憶。我不知道我為什麼在這裡，但我覺得我應該在這做一杯咖啡......唔，你想喝一杯嗎？", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咖啡只有親手沖煮才能做出靈活美妙的風味。讓我找找，新到的種子放在哪裡了，應該是我自己收起來的......", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是在什麼吉他的後面，嗯......說起吉他突然覺得有點生氣，奇怪，是什麼讓我心裡堵得慌呢？", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉他？生氣？您還好嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，可能是因為那個吉他看起來沒那麼有趣吧。", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請隨便坐，你等的人馬上就到了。", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要等的人......？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#11$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要等的，還是在等你的？我分不清。", "name": "咖啡色的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1009_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，你在這。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......記得您。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上好，阿黛爾，很抱歉我來遲了——今天有記得吃早餐嗎？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，吃了。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？您為什麼問這個？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乖孩子。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經換好了衣服，是準備好了嗎？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衣服......？欸，這件外衣不是媽媽的......？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收拾好東西出門吧，我們一起購物，去買一些攀登火山要用的東西。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g2_siestacommercialstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$EyjafjallaDream_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽一點一點地墜了下去，沿路店鋪裡的燈光星星點點亮了起來。阿黛爾眼前有些模糊，她彷彿在某處某時見過這樣的天空。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞南境的那座小城，記憶裡校園通往家的路上，是不是也有這麼一小段街道？"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她甚至還記得那時空氣裡的味道。微微濕潤，帶著一點點陽光和植物生長的氣味，和現在的一模一樣。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，是你們的商場嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，在爬上火山前，我們需要先做一些準備。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，要準備的東西有很多，指南針、防護服、相機......如果要在山上過夜的話，還要帶上火石和帳篷。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，在這裡我們不用準備這些。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先要買夠的是“知識”，“勇氣”和“好奇”，看看價格買一樣就好，最後再買一點“好運”。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是“好運”很貴，又常常是賣得最快的，所以預算不夠的話也可以不用買。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣啊......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 60.0, "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_coin"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_coin", "loop": "false", "channel": "coin1", "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟綿綿的生物抖了抖身子，幾枚汽水瓶蓋從她的絨毛裡掉了出來。叮鈴哐啷，瓶蓋落入商人的口袋。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1011_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您的慷慨！", "name": "精明的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1011_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......我可能還需要再買一點“勇氣”。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "登上火山的“勇氣”已經足夠，我需要一點離開家的“勇氣”。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 8.0, "times": 80.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_coin"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_coin", "loop": "false", "channel": "coin2", "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_coin", "loop": "false", "channel": "coin3", "delay": 1.1}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟綿綿的生物再次抖了抖身子，幾枚瓶蓋掉了出來。商人張開口袋，等待著更多。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1011_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不夠呢，不夠呢。", "name": "精明的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1011_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "口袋沒有滿起來，口袋沒有滿起來，“勇氣”不能給你了。", "name": "精明的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1011_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "買不到“勇氣”的話，您是不是就沒辦法爬火山了？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#11$2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係的，阿黛爾，這樣的事總會發生。我已經漸漸地習慣於自己給自己找尋“勇氣”了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，我們走吧。而且，這一路我們都要小心點，要看好自己的東西。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "東西？可是我沒有帶什麼東西呀。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人想要偷走“照片”。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟在我後面，幫我看好我的包裹好嗎？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您剛剛說什麼？我沒有聽清......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣下去可不行，阿黛爾，這個給你。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 60.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟綿綿的生物抖抖身子，從她身上掉下一團羊毛。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，把它戴一點在耳朵上，你就能聽到了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我們還要去找下一位。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g2_siestacommercialstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一隻軟綿綿的生物正在用照片覆蓋住面前的窗戶，聽到腳步聲，他回過了頭。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毛絨絨的背部挪了又挪，遮住了那面貼上了照片的窗。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，嗯......你們......你們終於來了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要做的準備很多，天氣怎麼樣？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天上雲很厚，恐怕很快就要下雨了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還有時間嗎？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會有很多了，我們要快點走才行。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾看了看天空，天上並沒有什麼雲朵。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......需不需要我去買把傘？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，阿黛爾。你看，我就是傘。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“照片”不能被淋濕，也不能被別人偷走，我會把它好好地藏在我的包裹裡。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“照片”是什麼？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，我希望你可以永遠都不知道那是什麼。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果知道了，那也是在很遠很遠的以後。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚴肅的生物垂下了頭。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我們待會兒要往上走，上面是我們要去的地方。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在的羊毛還不太夠，給，阿黛爾，這團是我的。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸......？好、好的。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個軟綿綿的生物看上去小了一圈，阿黛爾則看上去像是他們之中的一員一樣。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.8, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.8, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dream", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,30", "duration": 4.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,30", "duration": 4.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,30", "duration": 4.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......喔！這些羊毛好像在帶著我往上蹦？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就說明，我們的旅程就要開始了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面的風景怎麼樣？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在雨落下之前都是很好的。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的心情怎麼樣？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在雨落下之前都是很好的。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，你呢？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，你現在，應該心情還不錯？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bleatone", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1004_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那隻瘦小的生物正跟著他們，一點一點地跳了起來。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順著街道，順著燈光，順著雲朵和星星，它努力地越跳越高。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇......它看起來強壯了不少。", "name": "阿黛爾"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它會和我們一起嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟綿綿的生物沒有回答，她咬住阿黛爾的衣角，叮、咚、叮、咚，他們踩著燈光。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g4_siestanewstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾覺得自己像是飛了起來，街上人來人往，不，或許應該說是羊來羊往。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sheeprun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——喔！小心一點跑，你撞到人啦。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面在賣花！我要快點去。", "name": "快樂的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不要急，你的彩虹都跑歪了，來，我幫你重新戴好。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rubwool", "loop": "false", "channel": "wl", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wl", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-70,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-70,0", "posto": "-70,-35", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-70,-35", "posto": "-70,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴好啦，走吧。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，再見，再見！", "name": "快樂的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sheeprun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1010_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻又一隻小黑羊穿梭在街道上，進出於店面中，夜晚的街道已經變成了另一種樣子。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾回頭尋找著被小黑羊沖散的兩位同伴，一個轉身，軟綿綿的生物正在她的背後靜靜地等著。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像他們已經在這裡等了無數年一樣。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g4_siestanewstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，這次回去，你要種一顆小石頭。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小石頭？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，就像我們之前種下過一塊小石頭一樣。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們把它種在土地裡，本來地下很黑，但它遇到了很多各種各樣的石頭。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我猜，是因為你買到了很多“運氣”給它嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向著更加遙遠的天空，兩隻軟綿綿的生物不斷地向上蹦去。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾站在他們中間，伸出雙手牽住他們身上的羊毛。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......也有這個原因，不過更主要的是，我每天都在給它澆灌“愛”。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有“回憶”。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些也是在商店買來的嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，小傢伙，“愛”和“回憶”是我們自己的寶物。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們會生長在你走過的路上，你的懷抱裡，還有你親吻過的臉頰上。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是它們有時候會被我們忽視掉，所以我們總是會很努力地去找。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那塊小石頭在地底跑過了很多座山，也跟著河流流過很多地方。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它磕磕碰碰，最後我們發現，我們已經不知道它去哪裡了。我們弄丟了它。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們......因為失去它很傷心嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#2$2"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們很後悔。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我們不應該把它種下，又或許應該把它種在我們能看得到的地方。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一塊石頭都是獨一無二的，我們弄丟了屬於我們的小石頭。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我記得，最後它變成了岩漿，熱乎乎的，我們都很喜歡。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我們都很喜歡。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就已經很好了......它最後成功地變成了岩漿，你們也一直沒有忘記它。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這顆小石頭已經足夠幸運了。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是夢吧，是夢，是故事。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盤旋在腦子裡，需要我們說給你聽。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，如果你們有一天再看到這顆石頭，你們還會認出它嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，我的小傢伙。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還會認出它嗎？", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，它已經變成了更絢麗的岩漿，赤紅的、熱烈的，不會回頭地向前奔湧而去了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不會再遇到它，我們只會在它的身後。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它會去到我們從未去過的地方，看到我們從未看到的景象。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們只需要記得這個故事，把它講給你。你也要種下一顆屬於你的小石頭，然後看著它生根發芽，看著它遠去。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，阿黛爾，我們已經到頂了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小石頭也已經變成了岩漿，馬上要噴發了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這個故事也要結束了嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並沒有，這只是個開始。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它會變成一朵雲，然後落回地面。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不再是塊石頭，而是一捧暖洋洋、白乎乎的火山灰。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1006_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種有營養的，能讓土地開出花的火山灰，就是由小石頭變成的。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的小石頭，它會回來的。在某一天，等到那時，我們就能再次看到它。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會很久嗎，還是很快......？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我們都不知道。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，阿黛爾，拉住我，我們也要變成雲，然後落回地面。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要一起飛下去了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾擁住身邊的生物，試探著邁出一步——"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她向下墜落，但是，緩慢地，輕飄飄地，這更像是飄落。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g2_siestacommercialstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到自己的頭髮飛揚起來，看到其他的小黑羊正圍著店鋪的燈火輕盈地躍起。"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身上的羊毛托舉著她，包裹著她，是已經在記憶深處的兒時，父母托住她，將她向著天空拋起，去捉天上的星星。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她掉落到羊毛上，身下的羊毛軟軟的。星星落到她的眼睛裡，她的眼睛熱熱的。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街道上的影子來來往往，阿黛爾試圖站起身子，她很想把這種奇妙的感覺告訴身邊這兩隻軟綿綿的生物。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......我......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們接下來要去哪裡？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛在上面的時候，我看到遠處還有幾家商店，還有不少小鋪，我們要去逛逛嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去看看哪裡還能找到汽水瓶蓋，這樣我們就能買到想要的東西了。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾的呼吸急促起來，她有些激動。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那隻小黑羊說前面還有賣花的，小時候我的床頭會有母親放的花，你們喜歡花嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種小小的，白白的花朵，和你們很像。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，就和那隻小黑羊一樣。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟綿綿的生物沉默了，他們不再回話。"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天上的星星暗下去，又亮起，他們開了口。"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小傢伙......", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，床頭的花真的很好聞，我也很喜歡。", "name": "溫和的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我去買來，給你們編一個花環吧！", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們在這裡等我一下，我好久沒有編過花環了，我......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1016_agoat2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾剩下的話哽在喉嚨中，她看到軟綿綿的生物已經停下了跟著她的腳步，法杖上的花葉正圍著他們飛舞。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們退後幾步，身影融進夜色。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback2", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.8, "g": 0.8, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "41_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 10.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.8, "g": 0.8, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，阿黛爾，我們該走了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雲已經聚集了，雲不會再散開了。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，到時間了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們要到哪去？", "name": "阿黛爾"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要在雨落下來之前到火山上去。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要去到火山上。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要去火山......你們是會......", "name": "阿黛爾"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，阿黛爾，雨快要落下來了。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不去的話，之前做的一切都會失去意義。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留在低窪的地方，是會被淹沒的。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，你要走到山頂去。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡有很美麗的風景，還有真相。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，我希望，你可以保持單純，專注。", "name": "嚴肅的生物"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這片大地並不純粹，但沒有什麼應當干擾一個求知者尋找答案的心。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們想與你一同拓寬人類知識的邊界。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們在為此努力著，而你也一定可以站在我們的肩膀上，看到一片更清晰明瞭、更可愛的大地。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾......", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，阿黛爾。", "name": "溫和的生物"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}